Assets At-A-Glance






The legacy Sunoco Logistics assets include the following:

Approximately 5,900 miles of crude oil pipelines
Approximately 1,800 miles of refined product pipelines
Approximately 900 miles of NGLs pipelines
Approximately 50 million barrels of total terminal capacity
Ownership interests in 12 products and crude oil pipelines
Full service Butane Blending at terminals and pipelines featuring patented, automated technology













