In the Community

	We believe it is important to give back to the communities we serve. That is why we are dedicated to helping organizations like Philabundance and the American Red Cross to provide assistance to those who need it most.
Learn more





Health, Environment & Safety

	Sunoco's success has always been built on a foundation of safe, reliable and environmentally sound operations.
