Sunoco

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Sunoco Logistics Partners, L.P.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the U.S. oil company. For the unaffilated Canadian oil company, see Suncor Energy.
Not to be confused with Sonoco, a packaging products company.

Sunoco Inc.





